   window.initGradientEffect = function () {

            if ($(".context-facets-filters") && $(".context-facets-filters").length > 0) {

                let scrollExists = $(".context-facets-filters")[0].clientWidth < $(".context-facets-filters")[0].scrollWidth;

                if (!scrollExists) {
                    $(".context-facets-filters").parent().removeClass('section-fade-effect');
                    return;
                }

                $(".context-facets-filters").scroll(function () {

                    var maxScrollLeft = $(this)[0].scrollWidth - $(this)[0].clientWidth;
                    var leftPosition = $(this)[0].scrollLeft;

                    if (leftPosition >= (maxScrollLeft - 5)) {
                        let hasClass = $(this).parent().hasClass('section-fade-effect');
                        if (hasClass) {
                            $(this).parent().removeClass('section-fade-effect');
                        }
                    } else {
                        $(this).parent().addClass('section-fade-effect');
                    }
                });
            }
        }

        $(document).ready(function () {

            const extendedTableZoomElements = document.querySelectorAll('.extended-table-zoom');
            if (extendedTableZoomElements && extendedTableZoomElements.length > 0) {
                window.Stickyfill.add(extendedTableZoomElements);
            }

            const socialMediaSideBarContainerElement = document.querySelectorAll('.social-media-side-bar-container');
            if (socialMediaSideBarContainerElement && socialMediaSideBarContainerElement.length > 0) {
                window.Stickyfill.add(socialMediaSideBarContainerElement);
            }
        });
  </script>
